## Campaign Setup Workflow

Build out a structured, trackable campaign:

- [ ] 1. Platform selection: Choose platforms based on audience and objectives
- [ ] 2. Campaign structure: Define campaign, ad group, and ad hierarchy
- [ ] 3. Targeting setup: Configure audience targeting parameters
- [ ] 4. Budget & bidding: Set budgets and choose bidding strategy
- [ ] 5. Tracking implementation: Set up conversion tracking and UTM parameters
- [ ] 6. Ad scheduling: Configure dayparting and flighting if applicable
- [ ] 7. Creative brief delivery: Issue briefs to creative team
- [ ] 8. QA review: Verify all settings before launch

## Key Inputs
- Client: {{client_name}}
- Objective: {{campaign_objective}}
- Target audience: {{target_audience}}
- Budget: {{budget}}
- Timeline: {{campaign_dates}}
